<p>For media enquiries, please contact:</p>

<p>Tel: +44 (0)1633 814167 or (0)20 7034 2841<br></br>
E-mail: <a href="mailto:MediaRelations@ipo.gov.uk.gov.uk">MediaRelations@ipo.gov.uk</a></p>

<p>For emergency media calls out-of-hours please contact the duty press officer at the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-business-energy-and-industrial-strategy">Department for Business, Energy & Industrial Strategy</a> on +44 (0) 207 215 3505.</p>

<p>Please note both our press officer and communications team are unable to respond to general enquiries. 
These should be directed to our information centre:</p>

<p>Information centre<br></br>
Tel: 0300 300 2000<br></br>
E-mail: <a href="mailto:information@ipo.gov.uk">Information@ipo.gov.uk</a></p>

<p>There is a separate process to request the use of the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/use-of-the-intellectual-property-office-logo">Intellectual Property Office logo</a>.</p>
